msgid "**Experiments:**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../simulator.rst:106
msgid ""
"*Beginners*: Use beginner mode with standard settings (constant width, "
"mass balance gradient of 4 and ELA of 3000) and run the model with all "
"different settings for the slope and use the geometry plot for "
"inspection. Take notes on a piece of paper of the ice thickness, volume, "
"area and length at the end of each model run."
msgstr ""

#: ../../simulator.rst:111
msgid ""
"*Advanced*: Conduct the same experiment as for beginners, but "
"additionally switch on the timeseries plot. Also take notes of the "
"velocity and look how the parameters change with time in the timeseries "
"plot."
msgstr ""

